column5: I will let the pic speak for itself. Enjoy!
nice fish ! where did she come outa?
thanks guys, put up a decent fight too. Fish was caught out of one of the small lakes up by stoney  no real public boat launch btw.
Nice Walleye. Was it a Erie fish or northern lakes? Got any info?
what a beauty fish that is!  Congrats!  Cheers!
Awesome instructor Short story but very nice indeed!!!  Congrats Leechman
Great Fish Man, a Beauty Indeed.

the-instructor already explained that this fish was caught in zone 15, NOT 17 and is a legal fish to keep. Unfortunately, this post has been altered and some responses have been deleted so now it's hard to figure out what's going on
My apologies, I did not see where it stated zone 15, like you said, must have been a previously deleted post.  Still a nice fish.
seriously tho.. these arguments aren't needed, congratulate the man on his fish and move along. we should be cheering each other on, not putting each other down.
finally some one who shares my views
